OL,3,CFarm worker killed by fire he started
OL,4,Cto keep warm, family say
OL,6,FThe sister of a farm worker who was
OL,7,Fkilled in a fire says he started it
OL,8,Fout of desperation to keep warm and
OL,9,Fbelieves those responsible for his
OL,10,Fhousing did not "give value" to his
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FGrace Monte De Ramos Castrudes spoke
OL,14,Fexclusively to ITV News about her
OL,15,Fbrother, George Michael Monte De Ramos
OL,16,FCastrudes, 37, who died in January
OL,17,Fafter the flames got out of control
OL,18,Fand engulfed his accommodation in
OL,19,FJersey.
