OL,3,CFarm worker killed by fire he started
OL,4,Cto keep warm, family say
OL,6,FMr Castrudes moved to the island from
OL,7,Fthe Philippines and had been living
OL,8,Fand working on the La Valette
OL,9,FNurseries Ltd site in Grouville for
OL,10,Fthree years - which is run by the
OL,11,FBlake family.
OL,13,FHis sister says her family are
OL,14,F"seeking and shouting for justice" as
OL,15,Fthey allege poor living conditions and
OL,16,Fa low duty of care.
