OL,3,CFarm worker killed by fire he started
OL,4,Cto keep warm, family say
OL,6,FShe says the family were unaware of
OL,7,Fthe fire or that Mr Castrudes was
OL,8,Flying unconscious in a critical
OL,9,Fcondition in Jersey's General Hospital
OL,10,Funtil a nurse answered his phone.
OL,12,FGrace explains: "We felt, 'What is our
OL,13,Fbrother's worth?'. For us, our
OL,14,Fbrother's life is really valuable, he
OL,15,Fis really important, he is loved by
OL,16,Fus, but this kind of person who is
OL,17,Freally responsible, they really don't
OL,18,Fgive any value to my brother's life.
OL,20,F"They really neglected George as well
OL,21,Fas George's family."
