OL,3,CFarm worker killed by fire he started
OL,4,Cto keep warm, family say
OL,6,FGrace says she had previously asked
OL,7,Fher brother to reconsider working in
OL,8,FJersey because she feared for his
OL,9,Fsafety and had concerns around the
OL,10,Fstandards of the shared cabin he was
OL,11,Fpaying #127 a week to live in.
OL,13,FShe adds: "He was telling us that it
OL,14,Fwas made of very light materials, it
OL,15,Fwas very small, it was very cold. It's
OL,16,Freally hard to bear that kind of cold.
OL,18,F"He said to me, even before he died,
OL,19,Fthat he would walk around because it
OL,20,Fwas just too cold."
