OL,3,CFarm worker killed by fire he started
OL,4,Cto keep warm, family say
OL,6,FAn inquest was opened to allow Mr
OL,7,FCastrudes's body to be repatriated to
OL,8,Fthe Philippines for a family funeral,
OL,9,Fwith the Coroner recording the
OL,10,Fprovisional cause of death as carbon
OL,11,Fmonoxide poisoning - no date has been
OL,12,Fset for a full inquest.
OL,14,FThere is no criminal investigation
OL,15,Finto the incident and while Jersey
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service says its
OL,17,Freport has now been finished, it
OL,18,Fexplains, "No further comment will be
OL,19,Fgiven as the inquest, which has been
OL,20,Fopened and adjourned, is yet to be
OL,21,Fheld".
